name: TreeListTest
description: Unit tests for TreeList operations including add, remove, indexOf, and iteration order.

test_cases.name: testAddMultiple
test_cases.description: Tests the addition of multiple elements to a TreeList and verifies their positions.

test_cases.name: testBug35258
test_cases.description: Tests the removal of an element from a TreeList and verifies the consistency of the ListIterator.

test_cases.name: testBugCollections447
test_cases.description: Tests the removal of an element from a TreeList and verifies the correct behavior of the ListIterator after removal.

test_cases.name: testIndexOf
test_cases.description: Tests the indexOf method of TreeList and verifies the index of elements after modifications.

test_cases.name: testInsertBefore
test_cases.description: Tests the insertion of an element at a specific index in a TreeList and verifies the positions of elements.

test_cases.name: testIterationOrder
test_cases.description: Tests the iteration order of elements in a TreeList initialized with another collection.

test_cases.name: testIterationOrderAfterAddAll
test_cases.description: Tests the iteration order of elements in a TreeList after calling addAll.

test_cases.name: testRemove
test_cases.description: Tests the removal of elements from a TreeList and verifies the positions of remaining elements.
